Enum SnomedInactivationPlan.InactivationReason

    SnomedInactivationPlan

    public static enum SnomedInactivationPlan.InactivationReason
extends java.lang.Enum<SnomedInactivationPlan.InactivationReason>
    Enumeration representing the reason of the SNOMED CT concept inactivation.

    The following reasons are available:

    • Duplicate
    • Outdated
    • Ambiguous
    • Erroneous
    • Limited
    • Moved elsewhere
    • Pending move
    • Retired

    Note that "Pending move" is present for completeness, however the process requires the concept to stay active, and so can not be handled by SnomedInactivationPlan correctly at this time.

    See Also:
    SnomedInactivationPlan
